<div class="container">

    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    <p>
        We are a small, independent reptile rescue operating from a home-based setup in Central Florida.
        Our focus is quality care over quantity.
    </p>

    <h2>What We Do</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Rescue unwanted reptiles</li>
        <li>Provide rehabilitation and proper husbandry</li>
        <li>Rehome to responsible keepers</li>
        <li>Educate the public on reptile care</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Core Belief</h2>
    <p>
        Every reptile deserves proper heat, proper care, and a second chance.
    </p>

